textBeforeTable: Compare Deer Away® Ready-to-Use Container Sizes Deer Off® is like a deer-proof fence that also keeps out smaller critters like rabbits and squirrels, which means you can use this one formula to save your plants from three of the most common garden nuisances. Repel Rabbits and Squirrels Too! Deer Off® is rain-resistant and gives you season-long control. Plus, it lasts up to 90 days - over twice as long as the competition - so you can spend less money and time reapplying. Weather-Resistant Protection That Lasts Up to 3 Months Watch the video to learn more about the formula » Deer Off® dries odorless to humans. Deer Off® contains putrescent egg, which repels deer and other animals by targeting their heightened sense of smell. Its odor warns animals of nearby predator activity, because it mimics that of decaying prey. This causes deer to immediately want to flee to safety. As a second layer of protection, Deer Off® also contains two powerful taste deterrents - garlic and capsaicin.
